@sttts these three lines are new. This fix the fake client in case there is no types requires clients in a group. In this case, the imported package is not referenced in the generated fake client, so there will be a compile error.

See the generated diff for the new event API:
https://github.com/caesarxuchao/kubernetes/commit/c984554789f0f05578880bf8659d667e218f28f9#diff-28a38b2d953d816541c1c2508844e543L22

